{"tid":2063192,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★保就業計人頭--71歲清潔工遭解僱，僅有2、3萬積蓄，需支付現居內地丈夫的醫藥費","createTime":"2020-06-13T17:09:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T16:33:55.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"faeb4eeceed175ce739b1b31fa686f335a9feca9","tid":2063192,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T17:09:09.000Z","msg":"求助個案之一的71歲張婆婆，在長沙灣街道任政府外判清潔工7年半，工作一直順利，惟上月中因天氣炎熱，反光衣清洗後未晾乾，疑因未有穿上反光衣工作，被僱主在未有警告情況下即日解僱。張婆婆指自己10多日以淚洗面，要看眼科醫生，現時視力仍模糊，未有找工作。<br />\n<br />\n她自居深水埗60呎劏房，月租要3700港元，未有強積金戶口，只能靠僅有2、3萬積蓄過日，更要支付<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>現居內地丈夫</strong></span>的醫藥費，但未有計劃申請綜援。張婆婆稱數月內有9名員工被辭退，大部分是年長僱員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200614/bkn-20200614003016525-0614_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200614%2Fbkn-20200614003016525-0614_00822_001.html&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJiukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=ac139bf9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200614/bkn-20200614003016525-0614_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f714009c669869d4b9126b4a637f0c6413e572be","tid":2063192,"uid":19454,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T17:09:40.000Z","msg":"71歲張婆婆  現居內地丈夫"},{"pid":"302b58c1c3f2424617eeefdfe2d898d18b362928","tid":2063192,"uid":38991,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T17:33:11.000Z","msg":"拎綜緩啦多鳩餘仲做"},{"pid":"71c450fdee7d11227392a2387a3f6fef0b23a1d5","tid":2063192,"uid":104804,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T18:02:17.000Z","msg":"張婆婆指自己10多日以淚洗面，要看眼科醫生，現時視力仍模糊，未有找工作。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一次聽"},{"pid":"59cbb5749280cfbc3e1810826b947807814fb2a0","tid":2063192,"uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike"